The paper focuses on testing deep learning models, which is a core topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also deals with image classification problems, which falls under the sub-category cs.CV (Computer Vision). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of metrics to select test data, which is related to software engineering and testing, and could be classified under cs.SE (Software Engineering). Finally, the paper proposes a set of metrics based on model uncertainty, which is related to control and systems engineering, and could be classified under cs.SY (Systems and Control).
